Thoughts on #SnydersCut
- excess doesn't always mean better
- Cyborg & Flash character dev clearly the A-game
- Snyder still doesn't get Batman
- Slow mo isn't cool as Snyder thinks it is

Overall, it balances the flaws of Whedon's but has its own shortcomings too. 

6/10 https://t.co/m3iYa1Jmv3
